Package: specteros-init
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, systemd
Description: Specteros OS Boot Orchestrator
 Handles boot orchestration and immutable root checks for Specteros OS.

Package: specteros-policyd
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, systemd
Description: Specteros OS Policy Engine
 Capability broker and permission policy engine for Specteros OS.

Package: specteros-shardd
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, systemd
Description: Specteros OS Shard Manager
 Handles persona shard lifecycle and context isolation.

Package: specteros-netd
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, systemd, iptables, nftables
Description: Specteros OS Network Daemon
 Shard-aware network policy and route manager.

Package: specteros-airlockd
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, systemd
Description: Specteros OS Airlock Service
 Controlled inter-shard transfer pipeline with metadata sanitization.

Package: specteros-auditd
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, systemd
Description: Specteros OS Audit Service
 Tamper-evident audit log service for security events.

Package: specteros-guardian
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, systemd
Description: Specteros OS OPSEC Advisor
 Local security advisor and risk alert system.

Package: specteros-updated
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, systemd
Description: Specteros OS Update Daemon
 Signed and reproducible updates with rollback support.

Package: gkctl
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Specteros OS Control Utility
 Command-line interface for managing Specteros OS services and shards.
